name: Good(ish) Music (Mens) Blue/Grey
description:
All shirts are 100% cotton and are printed on high-quality American Apparel tees.

Shipping:

All shipping has a flat rate of $5.00. We do not currently ship outside of the U.S. Please allow 5-10 business days for your shirt to arrive.

Payment:

We accept Visa, Master Card, American Express, Discover, or payments made though PayPal.

Returns:

If, for any reason, you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may return your unworn/unwashed item for a full refund. *Buyer is responsible for the return shipping costs.

Questions?

Send an email to: contact@goodishmusic.com
